overview: Six romper stompers invade Reno and turn the Biggest Little City in the World into party central. Storming into Reno from all across the country - Parker and Darius from Texas; Kaleb from NYC; Colin from Orlando; redheaded Elijah from Delaware; and Tony from Kentucky - this fresh class of young jocks is ready to raise hell and make their mark in the Biggest Little City in the World! So roll the dice and let's see who cums up the winner!
title: Road Trip 15: Snow Trip Reno
